summary: A RaceMenu Preset of my character, Calina
descriptionHtml:
[size=4]Description[/size]

This is simply a RaceMenu preset of my Skyrim character, Calina.

This Preset is designed for use with Human races (Nord, Breton, Redguard, Imperial). It will work with Elf races but may not look correct.

[size=4][b]Requirements[/b][/size]

[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/29624/?]RaceMenu[/url] by expired6978
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/68311/?]KS Hairdos - Renewal[/url] by Kalilies Stealthic Khaos and Shocky
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/13722/?]The Eyes of Beauty[/url] by Gabriel Mailhot

[size=4][b]Installation[/b][/size]

Unzip the file and drop it into your Skyrim\Data folder. Or use your preferred Mod Manager

[size=4][b]Unistallation[/b][/size]

Remove the file "Calina (Nephenee13).jslot" from this directory:
Skyrim\Data\SKSE\Plugins\CharGen\Presets

[size=4][b]Mods Used in Screenshots[/b][/size]

Body - Unified UNP Bodyslide
Body Preset - [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/71548/?]Enhanced DMRA[/url]
Skin Texture - [url=http://skydevgru.tumblr.com/post/120815089513/graphene-sr-3c-20-mission-humanoid-female]Graphene UNP Block Update[/url]
Prison Clothes - [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/47376/?]UNP Mini Dresses[/url] and [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/69880/?]UUNP Mini Dresses Conversion
[/url]Huntress Outfit - [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/57909/?]Sotteta Huntress Armor UNP[/url] and [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/68670/?]Sotteta Huntress UUNP Conversion[/url]
ENB - [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/56020/?]AIR ENB
[/url]
